The paper deals with machine learning and specifically addresses the issue of training set bugs, which is a common problem in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses the need for human experts to verify the potential bugs, which suggests a connection to the sub-category cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
